    • Constructor Detail

      • MainFrame

        public MainFrame(ImageDataStorage imgDataStorage)
        Loads all the objects needed for working with images, creates a new PCDmouse click listener what will Initializes all the image panes,components,table, table model.

        Enables different functions for the GUI Adds ClickListener, addCompoment listener, MouseWheel listener, Mouse Motion listener In case of errors, it catches the exception such as ClassNotFoundException, InstantiationException, IllegalAccessException,UnsupportedLookAndFeelException UnsupportedFlavorException IOException and adds it to the Logger object

        Parameters:
        imgDataStorage - the object responsible for image data storage and manipulation

      • MainFrame

        public MainFrame(ImageDataStorage imgStore,
                 String projectFile)
        This constructor is called when there is an already existing project created.
        Parameters:
        imgStore - ImageDataStorage object containing data about the images.
        projectFile - String which is the name of the project.
